hopobject.body: Could you please repeat that? fluticasone furoate nasal spray dosage I understand that most plans have the one free or even two free doctors visits a year but for a good cost comparison I believe one needs to figure one unplanned visit to the doctor (not emergency but doctor…such as someone getting a cold or flu) wherein the deductible has to be met on most (if not all??) plans prior to insurance covering that extra visit.
